**Property tax** is levied annually by municipal corporations on residential and commercial properties based on the Annual Rental Value (ARV) or Unit Area Value. Rates differ significantly: BBMP (Bengaluru) uses a unit area system, MCGM (Mumbai) uses rateable value, and NDMC/MCD (Delhi) use both. Timely payment avoids 2% monthly penalty and qualifies for a 5–10% early payment discount.
